description:
Hello, I'm Agatha! 😊

Like and subscribe for more videos!! Thanks for watching :)

I'm excited to share this video with you because I'm going to follow TikTok makeup hacks!! I just want to make a quick disclaimer that I of course messaged and asked permission from the people who are in the TikTok videos that I showed.  

If you have some suggestions, please leave them below and I would love to do them soon (try ko talaga promise) 

Products used:
Dasom Skincare Primer
Loreal Infallible Full Wear Concealer in Cashew
Maybelline Hyper Curl Mascara
Vice Cosmetics BT21 eyeshadow palette
Benefit Hoola Bronzer
Detail Cosmetics Contour and Highlighter Stick
Detail Cosmetics SuperFine Liner in Mocha
Squad Cosmetics Multi-Purpose Mousse Cream in Bubbly
Generation Happy Skin Water Gel Lip and Cheek Tint in Tough
Generation Happy Skin On The Glow Blush in Glowing
Brow Bizz Brow Soap in Clear

Let's be friends!
